Who we are

Healthy People, Sustainable Future!

MCH is bridging the gap between substandard and optimal health care by providing personalized and integrated health care access and coaching.

Our approach is to build and enable a clinically integrated network using technology, team-based care and a unique disease management and prevention approach. Helping healthcare providers to better provide and deliver quality care. This will be done using a Patient Centered Medical Home (PCMH) care delivery model.

We are focused on improving health outcomes and quality of life from an individual perspective as well as across an entire population. We want to empower communities to be effectively involved in the provision of their own healthcare.

We recognize that improved health outcomes can only be achieved by combining the clinical guidance of skilled physicians with a technology enabled disease management and prevention team; hence our partnership with physicians to improve the health of the population.goals, and heal your body to live your best life possible.

Methodology

Our Methodology

  • Assess health risks through the use of predictive modeling and analysis 
  • Identify healthcare needs using innovative diagnostics 
  • Engage the patient through multiple technology and clinical platforms 
  • Modify health seeking behavior through personalized coaching 
  • Improve health outcomes through direct dedicated care 
  • Lower healthcare cost
